{
  "stem": "5740.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And a couple of days later, I thought, maybe my mother made the parcel.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was a double decker.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I never could find anymore this box.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I never know what my mother sent.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was stupid.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it doesn't matter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It-- this doesn't matter, only if there with things of some sentimental value, which would matter to me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After that, after your mother sent you the special box--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the letters and parcels stopped.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They stopped, the letters.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we became a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It became-- it changed to a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the same place all the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Always at the--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But, but the, the sort of--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had to parade naked in front of the SS men.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We, we had SS men, you know, [NON-ENGLISH] to watch us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To guard us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the food became less and less, the treatment became worse and worse.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The typhoid was just killing, left, right, and center, everybody, every one of us-- not everyone, because some survived.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The tuberculosis, people were dying on tuberculosis.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The bed bugs was eating us up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The bed bugs was something, the smell of the bed bugs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We, we-- there was very little opportunity to clean it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I still tried to clean the, the mattresses there that were full of straw, full of the bed bugs, but it didn't help much.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the worst thing was the lice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The lice.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know what this feels, lice?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This, the lice, which occur here, the pubic lice, and they-- half of them are in your body and half is out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they, they are so terrible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They, they, they-- you, you get meshuga from it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they drive you crazy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They drive you crazy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So itchy.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
